== Features ==

* Get text sizes
* Draw pixel matrix
* CMake install
* Zooming
* Mouse coordinates vs. layer coordinates
* Time / fixed FPS system
* setFill(layer)
* Gradients
* Window::setIcon()
* Layer3D...

== Drawing Primitives ==

* drawEllipse()
* fillEllipse()
* drawRectangle()
* fillRectangle()
* drawPolly()
* fillPolly()

== OpenGL ==

* Layers with pbuffers when supported
* Draw to non-root layer before update

== Systems ==

* Null
* XOpenGL
* OSXOpenGL
* WinOpenGL
* WinDirectX

